name: Cantina Brawl (V)
Lore: '''...watch your step. This place can be a little rough.'' The Mos Eisley Cantina harbors smugglers, thieves, cutthroats, criminals and bounty hunters!',
Text: 'If a battle was just initiated at an interior site where both players have a participating character armed with a weapon, your weapon destiny draws there are +1 (+3 if at Cantina) for remainder of turn.',
